    "red_box_keyword": "Leash",
    "serotonin_payoff_number": 98765,
    "phase_1": "Kya aapke paas hai yeh 'Invisible Leash'?",
    "phase_2": "Yeh aapko rok rahi hai, har din, har step par. Lekin kaise?",
    "phase_3": "Mujhe bhi lagta tha, 'business' ya 'creative ideas' sirf kuch khaas logon ke liye hote hain. Meri anxiety, mera overthinking... yeh sab sirf distractions the. Main hamesha darta tha ki log kya kahenge, kya mera product (jaise yeh special pet food) bikega bhi ya nahi? Raaton ki neend udd jaati thi yeh soch kar ki kya main sach mein yeh kar sakta hoon? Aap bhi shayad aise hi feel karte ho na, jab aapko ek naya kadam lena hota hai. Jab aapko lagta hai ki aapke paas saari information nahi hai, ya aapka product perfect nahi hai. Yeh 'invisible leash' aapke dimaag mein bandhi hai, jo aapko aage badhne se rok rahi hai.",
    "phase_4": "Sachai yeh hai ki woh 'Invisible Leash' aapki nervousness nahi, balki 'perfect-planning paralysis' hai! Jab aap 98765 chote steps ko follow karte ho, tabhi aapki sabse badi kamzori taakat ban jaati hai.",
    "phase_5": "Toh ab samjhe, woh 'Invisible Leash' jo aapko rokti hai, use todne ka raaz kya hai?"
  },
